 (g) GP shall
deliver to the Buyer copies of the certificates of good standing of each of Newco, the Company and all of the Subsidiaries, certified on or soon before the Closing Date by the Secretary of State (or comparable officer) of the jurisdiction of each
such Persons incorporation;  (h) GP shall
deliver to the Buyer a certificate signed by an authorized officer of GP, with respect to each of Newco, the Company and all of the Subsidiaries, with respect to (i) no amendments to the certificate of incorporation of such Person since the date of
