Agreement;  (i) GP shall deliver to the Buyer a
copy of the certificate of incorporation of each of Newco, the Company and the Subsidiaries certified as of a recent date by the Secretary of State of the state of incorporation of each of Newco, the Company and each of the Subsidiaries;
