Affiliate of the Company or any of its Subsidiaries (including GP or its Subsidiaries), other than the Company or any of its Subsidiaries; or  (xvii) agree to do any of the foregoing.  SECTION 7.2. Access to Information. From the date of this Agreement until the Closing Date, GP will
